<header>
    <h1>Automating Learning Systems</h1>
    <p>An interdisciplinary research group at Carnegie Mellon University exploring the intersection of Machine Learning, Systems, and Compilers.</p>
</header>

<div class="container">
    
    <div class="mission-box">
        <h2>Our Mission</h2>
        <p>The Catalyst group builds ML algorithms and learning systems that automate cross-stack optimizations. By co-designing hardware, systems, and ML algorithms, we aim to make the next generation of AI efficient, scalable, and accessible across all hardware platforms.</p>
    </div>

    <h2 class="section-title" id="research">Active Projects</h2>
    <div class="project-grid">
        <div class="project-card">
            <h3>XGrammar</h3>
            <p>Efficient, flexible, and portable structured generation for Large Language Models.</p>
            <div style="margin-top: 1rem;"><span class="tag">LLM</span> <span class="tag">Efficiency</span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="project-card">
            <h3>Apache TVM</h3>
            <p>An automated end-to-end optimizing compiler stack for deep learning on diverse hardware backends.</p>
            <div style="margin-top: 1rem;"><span class="tag">Compilers</span> <span class="tag">Open Source</span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="project-card">
            <h3>MLC-LLM</h3>
            <p>A universal solution allowing any language model to be deployed natively on various hardware and applications.</p>
            <div style="margin-top: 1rem;"><span class="tag">Deployment</span> <span class="tag">6G/Edge</span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="project-card">
            <h3>XGBoost</h3>
            <p>A scalable, portable and distributed gradient boosting library, used widely in data science challenges.</p>
            <div style="margin-top: 1rem;"><span class="tag">ML Systems</span> <span class="tag">Legacy</span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="project-card">
            <h3>TidalDecode</h3>
            <p>A sparse attention framework designed specifically for high-throughput LLM decoding.</p>
            <div style="margin-top: 1rem;"><span class="tag">Inference</span> <span class="tag">Algorithms</span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="project-card">
            <h3>TASO</h3>
            <p>The Tensor Algebra SuperOptimizer for deep learning that automatically optimizes graph transformations.</p>
            <div style="margin-top: 1rem;"><span class="tag">Optimization</span></div>
        </div>
    </div>

